titleInfo.title: Natures Way Marine, LLC v. EverClear of Ohio, Ltd. et al
titleInfo.subTitle: JUDGMENT in favor of Plf, Natures Way Marine, LLC, & against Dfts, EverClear of Ohio, Ltd., Nirk Magnate Holding Corp., in the amount of $205,512.00 & attorneys' fees are awarded to Natures Way Marine, LLC in the amount of $69,336.15. Prejudgment interest is awarded at an annual interest rate of 3.25%, & post judgment interest is awarded at the statutory rate of.22% as set out. Counterclaims filed by Everclear of Ohio, Ltd., & Nirk Magnate Holding Corp. are DISMISSED w/prejudice. Costs are to be taxed against Dfts/Counter-Claimants. Signed by Judge Callie V. S. Granade on 4/20/2015. (tot)
